error.message: Usage of deprecated trait Drupal\Tests\taxonomy\Functional\TaxonomyTestTrait in class Drupal\Tests\social_simple\Functional\TestSocialSimpleTestBase. Deprecated in drupal:8.8.0 and is removed from drupal:9.0.0. Use \Drupal\Tests\taxonomy\Traits\TaxonomyTestTrait instead.
Add core_version_requirement: ^8 || ^9 to social_simple.info.yml to designate that the module is compatible with Drupal 9. See https://www.drupal.org/node/3070687.
